    <entry>
      <title>搭建博客遇到的问题和解决办法</title>
      <link href="/2023/06/29/da-jian-bo-ke-yu-dao-de-wen-ti-he-jie-jue-ban-fa/"/>
      <url>/2023/06/29/da-jian-bo-ke-yu-dao-de-wen-ti-he-jie-jue-ban-fa/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在这篇文章我会记录我搭建博客并美化时遇到的问题，以及解决方法<!--（持续更新ing）--></p><hr><h4 id="npm安装没反应"><a href="#npm安装没反应" class="headerlink" title="npm安装没反应"></a>npm安装没反应</h4><p>解决办法：更换淘宝源</p><pre class="line-numbers language-markup" data-language="markup"><code class="language-markup">npm config set registry http://registry.npm.taobao.org<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="hexo-g-报错"><a href="#hexo-g-报错" class="headerlink" title="hexo g 报错"></a>hexo g 报错</h4><h5 id="can-not-read-a-block-mapping-entry-a-multiline-key-may-not-be-an-implicit-key"><a href="#can-not-read-a-block-mapping-entry-a-multiline-key-may-not-be-an-implicit-key" class="headerlink" title="can not read a block mapping entry; a multiline key may not be an implicit key"></a><code>can not read a block mapping entry; a multiline key may not be an implicit key</code></h5><p>解决办法：在设置属性后面加空格</p><h4 id="hexo-d报错"><a href="#hexo-d报错" class="headerlink" title="hexo d报错"></a>hexo d报错</h4><h5 id="Error-Spawn-failed-at-ChildProcess"><a href="#Error-Spawn-failed-at-ChildProcess" class="headerlink" title="Error: Spawn failed at ChildProcess"></a><code>Error: Spawn failed at ChildProcess</code></h5><blockquote><p>解决办法：</p><ul><li>删除文件夹 .deploy_git</li><li>执行命令 git config –global core.autocrlf false</li><li>然后就是 hexo clean</li><li>hexo g</li><li>hexo s</li><li>最后查看没问题就可以部署到github上了</li><li>hexo d</li></ul></blockquote><h4 id="博客无法访问"><a href="#博客无法访问" class="headerlink" title="博客无法访问"></a>博客无法访问</h4><p>上周我为了让博客访问速度加快一点，于是就把博客项目从GitHub迁到了vercel，以及使用cloud flare来提供CDN加速。部署完之后就等着一天之后自动更新dns，结果第二天cloud flare和vercel陆续给我发来了邮件说域名配置出错。今天看了cloud flare的提示，将指向vercel的dns服务器删去，马上恢复了正常访问🤣。</p>]]></content>
      
      
